gov.nasa.jpf.report

Class Publisher

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpf.report.Publisher
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConsolePublisher, XMLPublisher

    public abstract class Publisher
extends Object
    abstract base for all format specific publishers. Note that this interface also has to work for non-stream based reporting, i.e. within Eclipse (we don't want to re-parse from text reports there)
